            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p><strong>Track and field complex&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p>This outdoor sports facility features an extensive outdoor track and field complex featuring a lighted, international standard 400-metre polyurethane-surfaced eight-lane running track, along with multiple throwing and jumping event areas. These include high jump, long jump, javelin, shot put, hammer &amp; discuss.&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Sports fields&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p>The facility has three lit, premium-classed, grass sports fields, which can be used for a variety of activities such as soccer, lacrosse, ultimate Frisbee and special events.&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Mooney's Bay Ski Centre</strong></p>
<p>During the winter, the facility turns into a cross-country ski centre -&nbsp;<a href="https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-culture/recreation-facilities/sports-fields-and-outdoor-recreation#section-1bad2515-4bcb-4538-b7a9-63920e259dc9">Mooney's Bay Ski Centre</a>&nbsp;- featuring five-kilometres of track-set lit trails, for classic and skate-skiing, and includes a ski school for all ages and abilities.</p>
</div>
      

