            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h3><strong>2025 rates</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Fees shown do not include HST.&nbsp;</strong>Applicable taxes will be added during the payment process.</p>
<h4>Age and group definitions</h4>
<ul>
<li>Preschool: Ages two and under</li>
<li>Child: Ages three to 12 years</li>
<li>Youth: Ages 13 to&nbsp;17 years</li>
<li>Student: Full-time</li>
<li>Adult: Ages 18 and older</li>
<li>50+: Ages&nbsp;50 and older</li>
<li>Senior: Ages 65 and older</li>
<li>Household/family: Up to two related adults, with or without their child(ren) all living at the same address. Children must be age 25 or younger.</li>
<li>Groups: Ten or more.&nbsp;</li>
